  "closed_at": "2016-12-19T07:07:49Z",
  "body": "文档看的不太懂，自己试着写，不知道写法对不对。\r\nindex.html\r\n```javascript\r\nvar scrollEvent = new Event('iscroll');\r\ndocument.addEventListener(\"touchmove\",function(e){\r\n    var scroller=document.querySelector(\".scroller-element\");\r\n    var distance=scroller.style.transform;\r\n    scrollEvent.distance = distance;\r\n    document.dispatchEvent(scrollEvent);\r\n});\r\n```\r\nmain.we\r\n```javascript\r\nglobalEvent.addEventListener(\"iscroll\", function (e) {\r\n   console.log(e);\r\n});\r\n```\r\n如上代码，touchmove滚动的时候只打印了一次。\r\n\r\n看了globalEvent.js，好像也只是把事件转移到document，于是自己在console里写\r\n```javascript\r\ndocument.addEventListener(\"iscroll\",function(e){\r\n    console.log(e)\r\n});\r\n```\r\n滚动的时候能正常打印。\r\n\r\n看了很多代码，也只能想到这样来实现滚动的监听，还出了问题。不知道有没有更好的办法？",
